{"tid":1218422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想整盾牌比屋企小朋友玩, 有冇巴絲有具體設計?","createTime":"2019-06-13T15:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T12:26:27.000Z","uid":198200,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a707dedd7f1eb89ae5ff0a49e9e30a2d0b1e0d81","tid":1218422,"uid":198200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 家中小朋友睇完ENDGAME覺得CAPTAIN AMERICA好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話好想好似佢咁揸住盾牌四圍去, 但想型之餘又真係擋到下野<br />\n<br />\n暫時有兩個諗法<br />\n1.輕型盾, 可以一手穩固HOLD住, 另一隻手做其他野<br />\n材料可能用浮板, 木板, 木方縛埋做一塊 之類<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.cn.made-in-china.com/2f0j01evOaUsCECYpm/EVA%E6%B5%AE%E6%9D%BF%EF%BC%88YG001%EF%BC%89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cn.made-in-china.com%2F2f0j01evOaUsCECYpm%2FEVA%25E6%25B5%25AE%25E6%259D%25BF%25EF%25BC%2588YG001%25EF%25BC%2589.jpg&h=1a63cf37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再加一個索繩既HANDLE同 另一個手握既HANDLE 就VERY GOOD喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有其他OPTION可以令個設計硬淨D就更好<br />\n<br />\n2.長方盾, 面積可以擋到全個人, 一般一手HOLD到之餘, 有咩事可以靠另一隻手加強穩固度<br />\n材料可能都係木板木方搭下珍珠板, 瑜伽墊等等可以一大塊過既韌性物料<br />\n但有個好大既問題就係唔方便拎出街, 小朋友拎到出街都唔方便四圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就咁整好拎出街比人以為係高殺傷力武器就唔好啦<br />\n所以如果有設計可以令成個盾係可以向街組裝, 咁就非常好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時淨係諗到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇巴絲可以比多D貨, 小朋友追我星期日前要交貨喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65eeb77abe1ddd56f5d2284761151006c10684f3","tid":1218422,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:47:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba0cb09ba93569ac54fd1b255ff0e469068e9b4a","tid":1218422,"uid":61918,"like"